---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { site } from '../data/config.json';
import licenseLogo from '../assets/cc-by-sa-88x31.png';
---

<footer>
	<div>
		<section>
			<h2>About this blog</h2>
			<p>This blog is a forum for all of the technical rants, ramblings, and nonsense that I feel like throwing at the internet. Mostly, the content will be about programming, servers, computing, gadgets, and the internet. But sometimes you may find even more useless articles posted here.</p>
			<p>All opinions expressed here are my own and do not represent the views of my employer or any organizations that I am part of.</p>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="https://github.com/stevenbenner" rel="noopener">My GitHub</a></li>
			</ul>
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2>My feed</h2>
			<p>Since you've wasted this much time why not follow me on <a href="https://twitter.com/stevenbenner" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>, or subscribe to my <a href={site.rss}>RSS</a> feed? You'll probably be the first.</p>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="https://twitter.com/stevenbenner" rel="noopener">@stevenbenner</a></li>
				<li><a href={site.rss}>Subscribe via RSS</a></li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</div>
	<p id="copyright">
		<Image src={licenseLogo} alt="Creative Commons BY-SA License Logo" />
		Copyright 2009â€“{new Date().getFullYear()} Steven Benner. Except where otherwise noted, content on this site is licensed under a <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" rel="license">Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International license</a>.
	</p>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		position: relative;
	}
	h2 {
		font-weight: normal;
		margin-top: 0;
	}
	div {
		background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top left, #626063 0%, #3a3a3a 40%);
		color: #aaa;
		padding: 2rem 0;
	}
	div a {
		color: #c3b59e;
	}
	div > * {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
	}
	#copyright {
		color: #676767;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		position: absolute;
	}
	#copyright a {
		color: #085982;
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	#copyright img {
		box-shadow: 0 0 3px #aaa;
	}

	@media (min-width: 600px) {
		div {
			display: grid;
			grid-auto-rows: 1fr;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			border-radius: 0 0 0.5rem 0.5rem;
		}
		div > * {
			padding: 1rem 3rem;
		}
		#copyright {
			padding: 1rem 20%;
		}
		#copyright img {
			display: block;
			float: left;
			margin-right: 0.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
